<% if @decision.deleted? %>
# Decision [deleted]

This decision has been deleted<%= " by the author" if @decision.deleted_by_id == @decision.created_by_id %>.

| created_by | @<%= @decision.created_by.handle %> |
| created_at | <%= @decision.created_at %> |
<% else %>
# <%= @decision.is_executive? ? 'Executive Decision' : @decision.is_lottery? ? 'Lottery' : 'Decision' %>: <%= @decision.question %>

| created_at | <%= @decision.created_at %> |
| updated_at | <%= @decision.updated_at %> |
<% if @decision.is_executive? && @decision.decision_maker_id.present? && @decision.decision_maker_id != @decision.created_by_id -%>
| decision_maker | [@<%= @decision.effective_decision_maker.handle %>](<%= @decision.effective_decision_maker.path %>) |
<% end -%>
| deadline | <%= @decision.deadline %> |
| time remaining | <%= @decision.deadline > Time.now ? distance_of_time_in_words(Time.now, @decision.deadline) : 'Deadline passed' %> |

<% if @decision.description.present? -%>
<% truncated_description = truncate_content(@decision.description) %>
## Description

```markdown
<%= truncated_description.gsub(/```/, '\\`\\`\\`') %>
```
<% notice = markdown_truncation_notice(@decision.description, truncated_description, url: @decision.path) %>
<%= notice if notice %>
<% end -%>
<% if @decision.is_lottery? -%>
## Entries

<% if @decision.options.empty? -%>
No entries yet.
<% else -%>
<% @decision.options.order(:created_at).each do |option| -%>
* <%= option.title %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% if @decision.lottery_drawn? -%>

## Final Results

Results are sorted by [verifiably random](<%= @decision.path %>/verify) values 🎲.

|   |   | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | `<%= result.lottery_sort_key&.slice(0, 3) %>...` |
<% end -%>
<% elsif @show_results -%>

## <%= @decision.closed? ? "Final" : "Current" %> Results

<% if @decision.closed? && !@decision.lottery_drawn? -%>
Drawing... Fetching verifiable randomness.
<% else -%>
Entries are sorted by random digits 🎲. Final order will be determined by verifiable randomness when the lottery closes.

|   |   | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|
<% if @decision.results.empty? -%>
| 0 | Add entries to see results. | 0 |
<% end -%>
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | <%= result.random_id.slice(0, 3) + "..." %> |
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% if @decision.statement.present? -%>

## [Final Statement](<%= @decision.statement.path %>)

<%= @decision.statement.text %>
<% end -%>
<% elsif @decision.is_executive? -%>
<% if @decision.closed? -%>
## Selection

<% if @decision.options.empty? -%>
No options.
<% else -%>
<% @decision.options.order(:created_at).each do |option| -%>
* [<%= @executive_selections&.include?(option.id) ? '✅' : ' ' %>] <%= option.title %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
## Options

<% if @decision.options.empty? -%>
No options yet.
<% else -%>
<% @decision.options.order(:created_at).each do |option| -%>
* <%= option.title %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% if @decision.statement.present? -%>

## [Final Statement](<%= @decision.statement.path %>)

<%= @decision.statement.text %>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
<% unless @decision.closed? -%>
<% if @current_user && @decision.created_by && UserBlock.between?(@current_user, @decision.created_by) -%>
*Voting is unavailable because <% if @current_user.blocked?(@decision.created_by) %>you have blocked the author<% else %>you have been blocked by the author<% end %> of this decision.*
<% else -%>
## Options

<% if @decision.options.empty? -%>
No options yet.
<% else -%>
Check ✅ all options that you would accept. Star ⭐️ options you prefer.

<% @decision.options.order(:created_at).each do |option| -%>
<% vote = @votes.where(option: option).first || Vote.new(accepted: 0) -%>
* [<%= vote.accepted == 1 ? '✅' : ' ' %>] [<%= vote.preferred == 1 ? '⭐️' : ' ' %>] <%= option.title %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% if @show_results -%>
<% if @decision.beacon_drawn? -%>
## Final Results

Results are sorted first by acceptance ✅, then by preference ⭐, then by [verifiably random](<%= @decision.path %>/verify) tiebreakers 🎲.

|   |   | ✅ | ⭐ | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | <%= (result.accepted_yes || 0) %> | <%= (result.preferred || 0) %> | `<%= result.lottery_sort_key&.slice(0, 3) %>...` |
<% end -%>
<% elsif @decision.closed? -%>
## Finalizing...

Results are sorted first by acceptance ✅, then by preference ⭐, then by random tiebreakers 🎲 (determined at close time).

|   |   | ✅ | ⭐ | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | <%= (result.accepted_yes || 0) %> | <%= (result.preferred || 0) %> | ??? |
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
## Current Results

Results are sorted first by acceptance ✅, then by preference ⭐, then by random tiebreakers 🎲 (determined at close time).

|   |   | ✅ | ⭐ | 🎲 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
<% if @decision.results.empty? -%>
| 0 | Add options to see results. | 0 | 0 | 0 |
<% end -%>
<% @decision.results.each.with_index do |result, index| -%>
| <%= index + 1 %> | <%= result.option_title %> | <%= (result.accepted_yes || 0) %> | <%= (result.preferred || 0) %> | ??? |
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

<% if @decision.statement.present? -%>
## [Final Statement](<%= @decision.statement.path %>)

<%= @decision.statement.text %>
<% end -%>
[<%= @decision.voter_count %> voter<%= @decision.voter_count == 1 ? '' : 's' %> — view votes](<%= @decision.path %>/voters)
<% else -%>

Submit your vote to see results. Votes are not anonymous — individual votes are visible on the voters page after you vote.
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<%= render 'shared/backlinks', resource: @decision %>
<%= render 'shared/attachments_section', resource: @decision %>
<%= render 'shared/comments_section', resource: @decision %>
<% if @current_user && @decision.created_by_id != @current_user.id && !@already_reported %>

---

[Report this decision](<%= @decision.path %>/report)
<% end %>
<% end %>
